This is a unique project from Worldwide Graphic Designers. On its 5th birthday WGD (WORLDWIDE GRAPHIC DESIGNERS) made a project that was carried out in a relay. 75 Designers from 25 countries participated in this project.

This is done by means of each designer who has finished putting his name in their own style, they must send it to another designer in a different country.
